          <line>AJAX</line>
          <line>Alas! My son, my son!</line>
          <line>TECMESSA</line>
          <line>Woe's me! Eurysaces, 'tis for thee he calls.</line>
          <line>What can he purpose?-Where art thou?-Ah, woe!</line>
          <line>AJAX</line>
          <line>Teucer, come!-Where is Teucer? Will he never</line>
