          <line>Alas! Woe, woe!</line>
          <line>LEADER</line>
          <line>Speak no proud words. Seest thou not to what woe thou art sunk?</line>
          <line>AJAX</line>
          <line>chanting</line>
          <line>O Zeus, of my fathers the sire,</line>
          <line>Might I but kill that hateful and crafty dissembler,</line>
