          <line>TECMESSA</line>
          <line>Since that is so, what shall I do to serve thee?</line>
          <line>AJAX</line>
          <line>Let me speak to him and behold his face.</line>
          <line>TECMESSA</line>
          <line>He is close by in the attendants' charge.</line>
          <line>AJAX</line>
          <line>Why is his coming then so long delayed?</line>
          <line>TECMESSA</line>
          <line>calling</line>
          <line>My son, thy father calls thee.-Bring him thither</line>
